  "title": "Baby Chicken Totems",
  "description": "Changes the model and the texture of Totem Of Undying to New baby chickens mob!",
  "body": "<p align=\"center\">Baby Chicken Totem replaces the Totem of Undying with an adorable custom baby chicken, complete with a fully redesigned model and texture.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/91c2c42449c35878e2fe24a7cdb239e29d4a22ee.png\" alt=\"True Doors Title\" width=\"900\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\">When held, it sits on your shoulder, adding a fun and charming companion to your adventures while keeping all the original totem functionality.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8d79adce9e611255070934fcad9c523426364660.png\" alt=\"Horizontal Line\" width=\"1000\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/07925ae37810489f3b39af9fa5c05ec557b1fa5f.png\" alt=\"Sample\" width=\"200\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/ecbe9e8d3fdc1b1c23cb7d64b3a023a38c1e40a8_0.webp\" alt=\"ALl Samples\" width=\"1000\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8d79adce9e611255070934fcad9c523426364660.png\" alt=\"Horizontal Line\" width=\"1000\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/0618fd10d0d75a8ac73497655364297a92c2b5ca.png\" alt=\"Supported Mods\" width=\"450\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\">This resource pack specifically supports First Person Mod.</p>\n<p align=\"center\">Many other mods are also affected automatically.</p>\n<p align=\"center\">When used with Hold My Items, the first-person held position may appear slightly above your hand due to the way that mod adjusts item rendering.</p>\n<details><summary>First-person Model mod:</summary>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/ce02ae0de0b803d78e0b7cccd861dcb5bb4bad2e_0.webp\" alt=\"First Person Mod\" width=\"450\"></p></details>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8d79adce9e611255070934fcad9c523426364660.png\" alt=\"Horizontal Line\" width=\"1000\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/9453e067f6a6baefcf6f67dd470602a87c00e68b.png\" alt=\"Particles\" width=\"450\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/035946c62289971076f90e523e84160440b66fbc.png\" alt=\"Polytone Required\" width=\"300\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\">The custom popping particle texture requires Polytone, as vanilla Minecraft does not support replacing the Totem of Undying's activation particles through a resource pack alone.</p>\n<p align=\"center\">Without Polytone installed, the custom baby chicken totem will still work normally, but the popping particles will use Minecraft's default texture instead.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/257980113241ed83ffbdde7004bfdd4169c57937_0.webp\" alt=\"Totem Particles\" width=\"750\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\">ALL OTHER TEXTURES AND STANDARD RESOURCE PACK FEATURES WORK WITHOUT POLYTONE AND LOAD NORMALLY.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/polytone\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/668456ea034890a9924fc93abbaf93241ecdf59d.png\" alt=\"Polytone Downloads Button\" width=\"500\"></a></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8d79adce9e611255070934fcad9c523426364660.png\" alt=\"Horizontal Line\" width=\"1000\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/baby-chicken-totems\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/9d3cd7c29b765ea051a12413a8580e6b002c04ff.png\" alt=\"Modrinth Download Button\" width=\"300\"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/patrickool/projects\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/425e2c3a8f7ca6ba05b2d4ea767640abc7b5ae71.png\" alt=\"CurseForge Download Button\" width=\"300\"></a></p>",
